it's kill or be killed out here!

don't you have better things to do?
tuv.seg: you know that your son could be in danger if the original makes it back home, right?
Sabes que tu hijo va a estar en grave peligro si el original logra volver a casa, ¿no?

or solid gold that you can lay your hands on right now.

He conocido a muchas personas que trabajan en esto…

don't worry. you all know as well as I do that...

that being said, you also have have no muscle mass to speak of...

Es difícil renunciar a esa mentalidad.
are you talking about jonny mountain?

Creí que iban a tomarme como rehén para tratar de extorsionar a los Cheonryong…

De verdad sabe cómo no dejar rastro. Tal vez sea un mercenario veterano o algo así.

tuv.prop: you let the kid go free?!
don't worry. if gramps won't come through for us, I'll think of another way--

the moment I saw that bastard laughing at our desperation, I swore to myself...

… y se entretienen viéndonos cazarnos y matarnos entre nosotros.

Y entonces, su prioridad va a ser sobrevivir, no matar.

Seguro escuchaste hablar de ellos. Siempre que hay una discusión sobre teorías de conspiración absurdas, alguien los menciona.

in the retreats, we're all equally guaranteed a basic standard of living.
tuv.seg: there was no threat to my survival.
No existían amenazas a mi supervivencia.

tuv.prop: I poured my entire life savings into this.
tuv.seg: I did it for my son...

tuv.seg: dammit, the reinforcements are already here!

...but the noise is actually coming from the inner walls.

para buscar la bifurcación del túnel…

tuv.prop: now, we're about to venture into the most cutthroat and lawless place on earth.
tuv.seg: we might end up in battle at as soon as we set foot into the place.
Tal vez tengamos que pelear en cuanto pongamos un pie ahí.

I'll get you home, no problem.
tuv.seg: so, why don't you jump ship?

that bastard john canty has gone out of his way to make things difficult for me...
tuv.seg: ...and return safely with the wristwatch in hand!
… ¡y regresar a salvo con el dispositivo!

tuv.prop: and now, he will escape the slums...

it might take us more time, but I think it would be safer if we all searched together.
tuv.seg: if it's so dangerous around here, is it really okay for us to split up like this?

¡Olvídate de esas utopías espaciales y ven a ver esto!

tuv.prop: looks like you've gotten mixed up with a real crafty bastard, edward.

tuv.seg: No hay duda, no estoy a salvo aquí.

I fucking knew it from the start!

fantastic! you're one meticulous villain, john canty! haha!

Cuando era niño, mi abuelo siempre hablaba sobre los 817.

Por lo que veo, hay un caos absoluto en el centro de Biringam…

tuv.prop: but I can guarantee you, no one else in the retreats will even entertain an idea like this.
will you accept the status quo and abandon your only shot at saving the people of the slums...
what happens now is up to you.

¡Vamos a saquear todo de camino a Solgaya!

tuv.seg: uh huh. yep, I can see it!

tuv.seg: it's a shame we gotta take him down.
Qué pena que debamos deshacernos de él.

tuv.prop: ...although he was ultimately fired for being a pyromaniac.

this time, there will definitely come a time when you have to pull the trigger.
this is probably the most valuable.

tuv.seg: why are people being made to fight and kill each other there?
¿Por qué los que van allí tienen que pelear y matarse entre ellos?

tuv.prop: ...we could stand to lose everything, even the money.

Por ahora, lo mejor que podemos hacer por Edward…

No estoy tan seguro de eso.

tuv.prop: ...but if I lose this one before the rest get here, we might be able to get away!
I can't find that fork in the road anywhere!
tuv.seg: are you sure we're in the right building?!
¡¿Seguro que este es el edificio correcto?!

tuv.prop: but we're not necessarily fighting to kill. we're fighting to survive.
tuv.seg: a gunshot followed by the words "he's down!" might get them thinking that they're next.
¡Un disparo seguido por las palabras “¡le di!” va a hacerles creer que ellos son los próximos.

tuv.prop: what a load of baseless nonsense!
tuv.seg: he's just some helpless kid from the retreats!
¡No es más que un niño inútil de El Refugio!

tuv.prop: well, it's not much of a plan.

No esperaba que tuviese semejante temperamento.

tuv.prop: I never thought the day would come when I'd need that old junkie's help…
tuv.seg: At least it looks like he has some kind of a lead…
Al menos parece que tiene una especie de pista…
they don't care if we die.

tuv.prop: can I blow up the rest?

tuv.seg: these morons are just after a quick payout, but even if they get their way...

tuv.prop: ...once you've gone back, how are you going to prove your identity?
tuv.seg: if you really were switched with someone who looks just like you...
Si de verdad te cambiaron por alguien que luce igual a ti…

this emblem belongs to one of the most violent gangs on earth.

tuv.prop: 내 아들 가벨과 리트리츠 부잣집 아들내미의 '바꿔치기'가 가능할지.

tuv.seg: maybe they're the remnants of that gang we crossed paths with earlier!
¡Tal vez sean lo que quedó de la pandilla con la que nos cruzamos antes!

tuv.prop: 그 어느곳도 때가 타지 않은 곳이 없습니다.

tuv.prop: I imagine those 817 bastards were set for life after ransacking this place.

tuv.prop: they placated us with phrases like "you too can enjoy life in the retreats one day“ or "you just need to pull yourself up by your bootstraps“ while exploiting us for all we were worth.

tuv.seg: but it didn't take long for us slum rats to realize...

what I do have in my possession...
Lo que tengo en mi manos…
...blew up our base camp and ran!

tuv.prop: I knew I'd have to draw them out into the open to hunt them down.

tuv.prop: it still stings a little, though.

tuv.seg: perhaps it's because both my father and my grandfather died in the bg...
Tal vez sea porque tanto mi padre como mi abuelo murieron en los CB…

if you think about it, your father is out there saving lives.
Si lo piensas bien, tu padre está salvando vidas.

tuv.prop: if we have a duty to protect human rights and dignity...
tuv.seg: and no one has the right to take another person's life...
y nadie tiene derecho a arrebatarle la vida a otra persona…

tuv.prop: we're lucky. those stupid drones can't seem to find us down here.
tuv.seg: hey, kid... you said you needed me alive so you could go home...

tuv.prop: did we miss a floor on the way down here then?
tuv.seg: I saw it with my own eye!

tuv.prop: well, there's no way he could've left brine.
sounds like you're in favor of the status quo.

tuv.seg: I guess you wouldn't have come up with an idea like switching your son to live in the retreats otherwise.

tuv.prop: don't worry about a thing. just rest up.

tuv.prop: 몰라? 어지간히 리트리츠에 관심이 없었나 보구만

you'd better get used to it.

if you're dissatisfied with your life...

Mi padre lo contrató para entregar e instalar purificadores de agua.

gramps and I will stay here and guard our supplies.

so I stationed snipers at optimal vantage points to set up an ambush along our transport route.

you'd better get used to it.

those who are superior to me.

let me know if gable wants one too.

고철수집 같은 거 안 해도 되는 거죠?

what the hell's gotten into you?

tuv.seg: ...to bring justice to this cruel, twisted world.

tuv.prop: 가족을 위해 사지로 뛰어든 영웅의 죽음이 아니었습니다.

was probably based on equipment fenced from the retreats.

tuv.prop: this had better not be another dud...

tuv.prop: I knew I was expecting too much from him...
...all we had were hatred and rage.
인류의 1퍼센트만이 리트리츠의 모든것을 누리고 산다는것이 더 말이 안되는거야.
it's not gonna be an easy ride.
looks like you're wondering why we seem to be preparing for a journey to hell and back.
he seems like a good guy...
don't worry about a thing. just rest up.
after that, I finally came to realize...
we demolished countless buildings, but the human heart cannot be shattered so easily.
tuv.seg: that we needed to change things, not destroy them, in order to rebuild.
de que teníamos que cambiar las cosas, y no destruirlas, para poder reconstruirlas.

tuv.prop: ...there's no such thing as undeserved good luck.
tuv.seg: the rest of his organs seem to be in pretty good condition.
El resto de sus órganos parecen estar en excelentes condiciones.

tuv.prop: they're pretty good at picking vantage points. they must be seasoned pros.
this would get you the house you wanted and more... what do you want to do?
dammit, this tunnel's like a damn maze!
I thought I heard gunshots, but it's suddenly quiet again.
I'll make sure you get whatever you want.
I'm trying to tell you that--
bah! what a load of crap!
tuv.seg: I never asked to be saved in the first place! you did that on your own, and now you dare ask for my help in return?!
¡Para empezar, no pedí que me salvaran! ¡Lo hiciste porque te dio la gana! ¡¿Y ahora me quieres cobrar un favor?!

tuv.prop: I know you came here hoping for a better life, just like me...
I'm sure the chief's been prepping for this day and night--
I knew it! you're trying to kill me!
dammit! there are more of them on my tail!
tuv.seg: for the last time, shut it!

tuv.prop: what I do have in my possession...

tuv.seg: … es un dispositivo móvil que va en la muñeca…
there's no way greenwood would fall for that!

tuv.prop: 이곳에서 보고 들은 것은 전부 허상이라고 생각해.
잘 안 되겠지만 그렇게 여기는 게 신상에 좋을 거야.
tuv.seg: it might be difficult to believe, but trust me, it's for your own good.
Puede que sea difícil imaginarlo, pero créeme, es por tu propio bien.
is it looking for this old man?

tuv.prop: now... where did you run off to?
perfect place for a little bit of fun, huh?
tuv.seg: it's so dark and cozy in here...
Este lugar es muy oscuro y agradable…
vulture scum like you always talk too much.

tuv.prop: 얄궂구만… 이렇게 비슷하게 생겼어도 한쪽은 슬럼가의 거지
tuv.seg: ...they're the spitting image of each other.
… son la viva imagen el uno del otro.

tuv.prop: He did swear on his wife!
희한하네요.. 아쉬울 거 하나 없는 남잔데.
tuv.seg: but you always seem to be complaining.
Pero siempre estás quejándote de algo.

tuv.prop: I'm glad I brought y'all along for the ride!
for a skinny runt with no muscles, he's pretty sharp!
tuv.seg: yeah, about that... we got lucky that retreats boy back there has good hearing. he's the one who found this place.
Sí, sobre eso… Tuvimos suerte de que el chico de El Refugio tuviese una buena audición. Él fue quien encontró este lugar.
I've got a wife waiting for me at home...!
